The NPE is occurring in this code snippet in SingleCounterBlock.populateMembers() because entry.getValue().getCounters() returns null:

{code}
      CounterGroup group = entry.getValue().getCounters()
        .getGroup($(COUNTER_GROUP));
      if(group != null)  {
{code}

Looks like the code needs to check for the lack of Counters from a task, or CompletedTask needs to make sure that getCounters() at least returns an empty set of counters for getCounters().  The latter is what TaskImpl does when the AM is running.
